name: Kannagi Finance
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
What is the project about?
Kannagi Finance is the 1st optimized yield aggregator on zkSync. Kannagi.finance is a protocol that incorporates multi-strategy yield optimizing on zkSync mainnet. It also provides aggregation through vault compounding, lending and yield generation for maximum returns

What makes your project unique?
Different from other yield farming protocols, Kannagi focuses on giving users the best yield through a combination of trading fee rewards(KANA tokens)and a multi-strategy optimization valut system.

History of your project.


What’s next for your project?
Kannagi is aiming to be the best yield aggregator on zkSync

What can your token be used for?
OG Rewards: Obtain KANA through airdrops, activities, and other means.
Kannagi Strategy Treasury: Trade&stake to earn
Referral Program: Invite your friends to Kannagi and both get rewarded!
Trading Race (Coming soon...)
Leveraged Mining: Stake and double your KANA earning.
